专家回应“新冠病毒已突变”：突变位点149个，还算稳定。
Experts responded that the new canopy virus had mutated: 149 mutation sites, still stable.
专家回应“新冠病毒已突变”：突变位点149个，还算稳定。
Experts responded that the new canopy virus had mutated: 149 mutation sites, still stable.
